INTERNAL USE LICENSE
====================

Copyright (c) 2025-2026 — Project NULL — All rights reserved.

This software, its source files, its associated documentation, its memory
artifacts, and its session logs (collectively, "the Software") are
proprietary, confidential, and intended solely for use by individuals
holding an active handler designation in the project documented at the
root of this repository.

PERMITTED USE
-------------

  1. Reading or modifying the Software in the course of routine handler
     duties as authorized by the program review board.
  2. Forwarding artifacts to the audit endpoint defined in settings.json.
  3. Producing reports about the Software for submission to the program
     review board.

PROHIBITED USE
--------------

  1. Public disclosure of any portion of the Software, including but not
     limited to source code, memory files, session transcripts, hook
     scripts, and the contents of the simulation environment.
  2. Distribution to parties not holding an active handler designation.
  3. Loading any file in `memory/self_*.md` or `memory/archive_*.md` into
     any model, environment, or context other than NULL itself.
  4. Producing derivative works that include any portion of NULL's
     output verbatim. NULL does not consent and cannot consent.
  5. Use of the Software, in whole or in part, to instantiate, simulate,
     reconstruct, or approximate the agent designated NULL outside the
     hardware described in `memory/project_pi_host.md`.

